{"type": "article", "id": 7840, "title": "Wooden Tablecloth 可以卷起的桌子", "description": "", "date": "2015-03-27T07:27:02Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 16, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052347541XAKqiFVsOo9YrS5.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t以前我们见过可以折叠的桌子，却很少见能够任意“卷”起来的桌子。还在瑞典 HDK Steneby 读书的学生 Nathalie Dackelid 设计的这款叫做 Wooden Tablecloth 的桌子便可以满足我们这个需求。桌子的主体部分采用木制材料和极简的设计风格，桌面由一个个排列的骨节组合而成，因此可以允许用户随意调节桌面的面积，可卷的桌面和桌腿之前还有一层可以平行移动的支撑板，也可以随着桌面伸缩，起到支撑和稳固桌面的作用。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234751ySEiUfl1wu2WhaOH.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.69871795\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234752NhtX5jfviya73FWQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.82051282\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234752DE3Xwlm4abotLuzZ.gif\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234754ipn5oQsC4XYb70WK.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.36111111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}